OL,6,F'I can breathe again,' Emma Caldwell's
OL,7,Fmother tells ITV News' Louise Scott,
OL,8,Fas Ian Packer is convicted of her
OL,9,Fdaughter's murder
OL,11,FA serial rapist has been jailed for
OL,12,Flife for the murder of Emma Caldwell,
OL,13,Fand has been found guilty of attacking
OL,14,Fmultiple other women.
OL,16,FIain Packer will serve a minimum 36
OL,17,Fyears for the murder of Miss Caldwell,
OL,18,Fwho went missing from Glasgow in April
OL,19,F2005.
