OL,6,FHer body was found in an isolated area
OL,7,Fof woodland, near Roberton, South
OL,8,FLanarkshire the following month.
OL,10,FPolice Scotland has apologised to the
OL,11,Ffamilies of Miss Caldwell and Packer's
OL,12,Fother victims for failures in policing
OL,13,Fat the time the crimes were committed.
OL,15,FPacker was first interviewed by police
OL,16,Fthe month after Miss Caldwell's body
OL,17,Fwas found.
OL,19,FBut the force turned their attention
OL,20,Fto four Turkish men, who appeared in
OL,21,Fcourt in July 2007.
