OL,6,FThis was one of Police Scotland's most
OL,7,Fexpensive and complex investigations
OL,8,Fever- with #4 million spent on
OL,9,Faccusing four innocent men, according
OL,10,Fto lawyers representing Ms Caldwell's
OL,11,Ffamily.
OL,13,FAfter Packer was released he committed
OL,14,Fsome "19 sexual offences or assaults"
OL,15,Fagainst women.
OL,17,FAssistant Chief Constable Bex Smith
OL,18,Fsaid in a statement: "Emma Caldwell,
OL,19,Fher family and many other victims,
OL,20,Fwere let down by policing in 2005. For
OL,21,Fthat we are sorry.
