OL,6,FDuring Packer's trial, the court heard
OL,7,Fa soil sample taken in 2021 from the
OL,8,Fsite where Miss Caldwell's body was
OL,9,Ffound was a "97% match" with soil
OL,10,Ffound in his blue work van, and Packer
OL,11,Fwas charged by police in February 2022.
OL,13,FPacker was also convicted of raping 11
OL,14,Fwomen among dozens of other charges,
OL,15,Ffollowing a six-week trial at the High
OL,16,FCourt in Glasgow.
OL,18,FIn total a jury found him guilty of 33
OL,19,Fcharges, relating to 22 victims, while
OL,20,Fthree other charges, the court heard
OL,21,Fagainst him, were not proven.
