OL,6,FHe denied all the charges in court,
OL,7,Faccusing all the women of lying, but
OL,8,Fadmitted during evidence he indecently
OL,9,Fassaulted Miss Caldwell. He said he
OL,10,Fwas "ashamed" of his actions towards
OL,11,Fher.
OL,13,FBut he denied murdering Miss Caldwell
OL,14,Fin his evidence, telling the court:
OL,15,F"It wasn't me who killed her. It
OL,16,Fwasn't me. I didn't do anything to
OL,17,Fher."
OL,19,FThe trial heard evidence from multiple
OL,20,Fwomen about Packer's brutal attacks on
OL,21,Fthem.
